WEBVTT

00:09:59.801 --> 00:10:05.123
(Aplauz)

00:10:07.986 --> 00:10:12.402
Nadajmo se, prikladan odgovor
na onaj divni citat,

00:10:13.386 --> 00:10:15.522
"uslišena molitva,"

00:10:15.546 --> 00:10:17.876
otvoren u svim smerovima,

00:10:18.773 --> 00:10:21.166
hvatajući plavu svetlost zore,

00:10:22.233 --> 00:10:25.916
belo dnevno svetlo nalik šatoru,

00:10:25.940 --> 00:10:28.858
zlatnu svetlost popodneva,

00:10:28.882 --> 00:10:31.664
i naravno, noću, suprotnost: